<doc>
  <member name="ID3D10SamplerState.GetDesc">
    <summary>
      <para>Get the sampler state.</para>
    </summary>
    <param name="pDesc">
      <para>Type: <b><see cref="D3D10_SAMPLER_DESC" />*</b></para>
      <para>A pointer to the sampler state (see <see cref="D3D10_SAMPLER_DESC" />).</para>
    </param>
    <seealso cref="ID3D10SamplerState Interface" />
  </member>
  <member name="ID3D10SamplerState">
    <summary>
      <para>A sampler-state interface accesses sampler state for a <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3dhlsl/dx-graphics-hlsl-to-type">texture</a>.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Create a sampler-state object by calling <see cref="ID3D10Device.CreateSamplerState" />.</para>
      <para>To initialize sampler state, bind the sampler-state object to the pipeline by calling <see cref="ID3D10Device.VSSetSamplers" />, <see cref="ID3D10Device.GSSetSamplers" />, or <see cref="ID3D10Device.PSSetSamplers" />.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d10/d3d10-graphics-reference-d3d10-core-interfaces">Core Interfaces</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d10/d3d10-graphics-reference-d3d10-core">Core Reference</seealso>
    <seealso cref="ID3D10DeviceChild" />
  </member>
</doc>